HEADWORD: Obolus
<hw>Ob"o*lus</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;<plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Oboli</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[L., fr. Gr. (<?/)]</ety>
<fld>(Gr.Antiq.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>A small silver coin of Athens,
